{"tid":2389953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE得獎9人合體秀美腿 子瑜雙腳大開火辣曲線全被拍","createTime":"2021-02-01T08:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T12:53:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8e235faa19842fbb3db1c188fe74ed31cdec5162","tid":2389953,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"南韓女子天團TWICE，昨日晚間(1/31)於「第30屆首爾歌謠大賞」上除了擔任表演嘉賓外也拿下「本賞」大獎，成績備受肯定。而TWICE上台時，9位成員皆穿著短裙一字牌開秀出9雙美腿相當吸睛，其中來自台灣的子瑜也難得站上C位感謝粉絲，加上好久不見的定延首次現身舞台，皆成為討論的話題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南韓於昨日舉行的「首爾歌謠大賞」（Seoul Music Awards）頒獎典禮，同樣受到新冠肺炎疫情影響改由無觀眾方式進行，但當日受邀的TWICE依然接續演唱了《MORE &amp; MORE 》與《 I CAN'T STOP ME》兩首夯曲，並榮獲「本賞」大獎令粉絲們相當開心。不過，最令粉絲們興奮的，莫過於先前因心理因素休息近3個月的定延驚喜現身。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/chaeyoung.fancams/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fchaeyoung.fancams%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9d1d6827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/chaeyoung.fancams/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n在稍早的紅毯上原本還是只有8人出面接受媒體的訪問，沒想到上台領獎時定延卻出現在舞台上並與成員一同演出，只見她穿著黑色西裝造型短裙配過膝長靴，並以腰封勾勒腰線，加上銳利的眼妝散發迷人魅力。不過，在表演途中定延還是被網友捕捉到緊張的神情，令粉絲們看了十分心疼，紛紛留言為定延加油打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jeongyeonmagazintr/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjeongyeonmagazintr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6134b1d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jeongyeonmagazintr/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，在受獎時身為「忙內」的台灣成員子瑜，難得站上C位代表團體公開向粉絲們致謝，而子瑜當天以俏麗的高馬尾搭配拼接造型短裙現身，白皙的直角肩與大長腿再次成為全場矚目的焦點，站在一旁的日籍成員Sana還露出「姊姊笑容」看著子瑜演說，溫馨的畫面使網友們看了忍不住大讚「Sana的眼神實在太有愛了」、「有種吾家有女初長成的感覺」、「子瑜今天還是一樣美」，也讓她們名字再次登上熱搜榜單中掀起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/with_tzuyuforever/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwith_tzuyuforever%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=73d0907a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/with_tzuyuforever/?utm_source=ig_embed</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tzuyu.pupe/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftzuyu.pupe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=7f23437a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tzuyu.pupe/?utm_source=ig_embed</a>"},{"pid":"a79b9521b064f580b6cdf00f538708eb198e1da3","tid":2389953,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"唔貼圖 屌你"},{"pid":"5b07d1e3f0d0eb195491617687384e564f899721","tid":2389953,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/0ef9e932aabbcefe94aa688f2c3496c1/1253e150e722f021-9c/s500x750/f2b257c8911cbec845939902f664d3dbeefe14c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F64.media.tumblr.com%2F0ef9e932aabbcefe94aa688f2c3496c1%2F1253e150e722f021-9c%2Fs500x750%2Ff2b257c8911cbec845939902f664d3dbeefe14c2.jpg&h=9d16f2e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/43fca4834fd5fe41a60b50e4edafe83e/8cede0d8f115bb70-5f/s1280x1920/18bb73894f1b9897875386ccdf3ecdaff71f49df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F64.media.tumblr.com%2F43fca4834fd5fe41a60b50e4edafe83e%2F8cede0d8f115bb70-5f%2Fs1280x1920%2F18bb73894f1b9897875386ccdf3ecdaff71f49df.jpg&h=86ee4c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72af95462175fd20b0f41fbb88895d3f1f7c8070","tid":2389953,"uid":136770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:57:18.000